The Lawrence and Mayo sunglass mela is here and I am at the City Center 2 store to check out their wide variety of sunglasses. You can find all the best luxury brands here like CK, Swaroski, Armaani and so much more! I loved their Vogue Sunglasses range and couldn’t get enough of it. After finding so many favourites, I finally settled on these perfect Lavender Sunglasses from the Vogue Range. They look so chic and are quite comfort. 

And thanks to the sunglasses mela, I got an additional 15% off on my purchase. You should also check out their endless range of sunglasses and get upto 40% off on all sunglasses at Lawrence and Mayo. So don’t forget to check it out.
